---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — HVAC Software Hub"
  description="How HVAC Software Hub earns revenue, our editorial independence policy, and FTC compliance disclosure."
  canonicalPath="/disclosure"
>
  <section class="container py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">How We Earn Revenue</h2>
        <p>HVAC Software Hub is an independently operated review site. We may earn affiliate commissions when you click on links to software products and subsequently make a purchase or sign up for a service. These commissions help us maintain the site and continue producing free, in-depth reviews.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p>Our reviews, scores, and recommendations are based on our own research and analysis. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content, scoring methodology, or the order in which products appear. We use a transparent, weighted scoring framework that is disclosed on every review page.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">What This Means for You</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Clicking an affiliate link does not change the price you pay for any product.</li>
          <li>We only recommend products we have researched and believe provide genuine value to HVAC and plumbing contractors.</li>
          <li>Not every product mentioned on this site is an affiliate partner. We include non-affiliate products when they are relevant to our readers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">FTC Compliance</h2>
        <p>In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's guidelines on endorsements and testimonials (16 CFR Part 255), we disclose our affiliate relationships clearly. Affiliate links are marked with appropriate disclosures on each page where they appear.</p>

        <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-8 mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Questions?</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or editorial process, please contact us at <strong>hello@hvacsoftwarehub.com</strong>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
